  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hot and cold buffet breakfast</p>
<p>Extended daily afternoon buffet with cake from 2-4:30pm</p>
<p>Five course evening meal with three choices of main dish</p>
<p>Complimentary tea and water for adults (12-8pm)</p>
<p>Weekly Austrian, international and dessert buffets</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Riml's Christmas Market on the 24th December 2024 afternoon with Gluehwein, punch, snacks and live music on the hotel terrace. Special gala dinner included in the evening.</p>
<p>New Year Eve gala party with live band in the golf park and Birdy Bar. All inclusive drinks during the party and finger food buffet. Large fireworks display from hotel terrace.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
